# ClinicHub - Conceptual Model

## Overview

The conceptual model represents the main entities of the ClinicHub system and how they relate to each other. This model focuses on the business domain without considering implementation details such as primary keys, foreign keys, or data types.

## Entities

- User
- Patient
- Doctor
- Specialty
- Appointment
- MedicalRecord
- Exam

